{"tid":2322120,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【回憶經典】重溫八九十後代 港產 聖誕節電影","createTime":"2020-12-12T05:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T05:37:15.000Z","uid":124655,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f82a678b3ee32a21874084f5aef488f4954d94dc","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:27:30.000Z","msg":"每年 12 月既時候, 就會見到大家講, 哇, 有咩聖誕節氣氛既電影好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多數大家都會推介海外電影, 其實, 8,90 年代既香港都拍過唔小有 聖誕節 或冬日味既電影,<br />\n等 觀察員 A 使出 copy &amp; paste 大法, 帶大家重溫呢啲屬於香港人回憶既  聖誕節電影 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>聖誕快樂（1984）</strong></span><br />\n一班卡士強勁的明星跟你過一個平凡得來非典型的快樂聖誕！<br />\n<br />\n電影於1984年底上映，當年席捲香港票房，是新藝城出品的又一賣座片。該片更是陳百強與張國榮兩大八十年代當紅偶像最後一次的合作。陳百強作曲填詞的經典歌曲《等》就是電影的主題曲。劇情簡單不過，是新藝城一貫的喜劇路數。麥嘉的老婆早死，獨力養活陳百強、李麗珍及光頭仔，自己找無老伴。那邊箱孩子鼓勵他追求隔鄰的女歌手徐小鳳，這邊箱他擔心張國榮拐走他的女兒；在混亂的求愛過程中，鬧出許多笑話。聖誕節的前夕，各人都拉開了自己的愛情好戲，有情人終成眷屬，佳節歡樂結局！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/resized/09dc6d5af4a2ba6d3e881c1e6a70cb99091115f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fresized%2F09dc6d5af4a2ba6d3e881c1e6a70cb99091115f0.png&h=5a17adcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/resized/b9319bb35900bc228f993b8a42ed93d776e817a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fresized%2Fb9319bb35900bc228f993b8a42ed93d776e817a4.png&h=103deab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/resized/592e5271df88763c0c3e9ac3328e1777e3a3e40e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fresized%2F592e5271df88763c0c3e9ac3328e1777e3a3e40e.png&h=7f5d7fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/resized/0fb823d9e146aef99199676fe1c44564a1a5a522.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fresized%2F0fb823d9e146aef99199676fe1c44564a1a5a522.png&h=4fbf6bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/resized/f485256bb1c2c98aed7543e67856e55b4a4f9cb8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fresized%2Ff485256bb1c2c98aed7543e67856e55b4a4f9cb8.png&h=5be0485b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2d768ca32b3f18f996396e80eaa8cba5c98d2ae","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>聖誕奇遇結良緣（1985）在刻板聖誕夜竟然遇到離奇遭遇......</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1985年香港德寶電影公司的創業巨製之一，當年由導演鐘志文，與林子祥、張曼玉、岑建勳幾位主角合作的一部精彩熱鬧的浪漫冒險喜劇。地下軍火專家圖謀不軌，三名互不認識的平凡寂寞人在聖誕夜目睹事件。兩名瘋狂殺手奉命追殺三名目擊者，他們惺惺相惜展開逃亡，過程中發揮同舟共濟的精神，結果以機智戰勝武力來化解危機。全片是典型以追殺為主戲的娛樂片，有不少驚險笑料。三位主角亦純真好玩，將寂寞都市人碰到戲劇性事情時的反應生動表現。特別一提，由林子祥主唱的電影主題曲《聖誕夜》，有林振強的詞，值得應節重溫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/resized/1e7a48d9bde3da85df813ced7f147faf463df874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fresized%2F1e7a48d9bde3da85df813ced7f147faf463df874.jpg&h=e5cfc842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.gtimg.cn/qqlive/img/jpgcache/files/qqvideo/hori/3/3yg28dv5zdwlgg2_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.gtimg.cn%2Fqqlive%2Fimg%2Fjpgcache%2Ffiles%2Fqqvideo%2Fhori%2F3%2F3yg28dv5zdwlgg2_a.jpg&h=33a9cc7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gtimg.cn/qqlive/img/jpgcache/files/qqvideo/3/3yg28dv5zdwlgg2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gtimg.cn%2Fqqlive%2Fimg%2Fjpgcache%2Ffiles%2Fqqvideo%2F3%2F3yg28dv5zdwlgg2.jpg&h=ae260c9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9aca00f28728be5f3af2549a6ac3da9e232b84e","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>秋天的童話（1987）聖誕，是屬於愛情的節日。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n超過三十年前的電影作品，是德寶的經典作品之一，由張婉婷執導，當年橫掃第七屆香港電影金像獎多個獎項。在美國的聖誕冬日，鍾楚紅與陳百強的情感崩塌，鋪墊周潤發因生情愫而作出的改變。船頭尺的草妄率直與十三妹的性情韻味， 明顯但不刻意。兩人自《女人心》後再次合作，點點火花教人看得舒服自然。二人交換禮物的一幕，至今仍令影迷心頭悸動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/public/resources/resized/2d9d9b59efed59aafcedda311af5b434c344ee29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Fpublic%2Fresources%2Fresized%2F2d9d9b59efed59aafcedda311af5b434c344ee29.jpg&h=c1d4ed12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nestia-food.obs.ap-southeast-3.myhuaweicloud.com/201909/30/b410b4fd1cc5c5e17bde5c6f3161de27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnestia-food.obs.ap-southeast-3.myhuaweicloud.com%2F201909%2F30%2Fb410b4fd1cc5c5e17bde5c6f3161de27.jpg&h=3bc4131e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=rjsm16/11980006q35pp580s912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Drjsm16%2F11980006q35pp580s912.jpg&h=510abb68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=25a7hr0/11sr0000ps99742750r5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D25a7hr0%2F11sr0000ps99742750r5.jpg&h=01127600&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98d0cb0f241c5376d58fc98111584f61480a85d8","tid":2322120,"uid":186125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:36:18.000Z","msg":"最記得沙示炸彈"},{"pid":"5596abe3f646b1586b879ef6068fd27804dac09c","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>吉星拱照（1990）佳節遇到對的人，得好好把握</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n杜琪峰出品，翻拍來自美國的電影《來到美國》，故事發生在香港的聖誕節時份，王子與灰姑娘大團員結局的愛情故事，片中男女主角於聖誕雨夜談情一幕，以及在尖沙咀節日裝飾下的場面，令人懷念當年香港耀眼奪目的聖誕燈飾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/men-image.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-12-24-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.44.51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fmen-image.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-12-24-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258811.44.51.jpg&h=9ce7a18f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.btdx8.com/uploads/2017/08/20170819170706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.btdx8.com%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F20170819170706.jpg&h=98c5e2a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ad79ad85ca1772b2f85bf65087a05eea59810c1","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>與龍共舞 (1991)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1991年上映的香港愛情喜劇片，由王晶導演兼編劇，劉德華、張敏、葉德嫻、吳孟達主演。葉德嫻憑藉該片獲得第11屆香港電影金像獎最佳女配角獎，張敏獲得其演藝生涯唯一一次最佳女主角提名。<br />\n<br />\n呢部個人最鍾意, 覺得最好睇既聖誕節電影 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-aliyun.awc618.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-aliyun.awc618.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F11%2F641.jpg&h=4e6476c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=1r27bkm/ctp-vzntr/96sn4pn387924p0oo82q79q2ro50p931.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1r27bkm%2Fctp-vzntr%2F96sn4pn387924p0oo82q79q2ro50p931.jpg&h=c66e46bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在1991年的電影中，《與龍共舞》是比較驚艷的，其中劉德華和張敏的出演，驚艷了無數的人，而電影中翁虹和葉德嫻也出盡了風頭。這對於任何人來說，或許都是一份積極的收穫吧！尤其是青年時代的女神，也曾放肆過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.agentm.tw/wp-content/uploads/%E8%88%87%E9%BE%8D%E5%85%B1%E8%88%9E_%E9%A6%96%E5%9C%96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.agentm.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%2588%259E_%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%259C%2596.jpg&h=8b67a8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在《與龍共舞》這部電影中，依舊是一個醜小鴨和王子的故事。這樣的故事，其實之所以能夠佔據人們的視野。關鍵就在於能夠傳遞出一種積極的因素：幻想世界。對於此，需要人們有足夠的認知，才能夠完成。<br />\n<br />\n1991年，已經過去了無數年，但這樣的電影還是歷久彌新，讓我們能夠充分感受到其中的無限可能。"},{"pid":"80347a3d03ce265ea707dd31fa748d2ade66521a","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>龍虎風雲 City on Fire</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n聖誕看厭了窩心電影，可以考慮陽剛味十足港產警匪片。1987年《龍虎風雲》由發哥周潤發及李修賢主演，是港產片最經典的臥底橋段，講述一班悍匪聖誕節搶劫金行。《龍虎風雲》獲當年金像獎9項提名，最後發哥奪得最佳男主角，林嶺東獲得最佳導演。今天重溫，除了欣賞當年港產片成功的動作場面外，還可以透過電影，了解80年代港九街頭風貌和情懷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-EWai4ZuukoA/TfGBWP9jtKI/AAAAAAAAAuQ/oRcjnKf__fA/s1600/1987%2BCityOnFire.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-EWai4ZuukoA%2FTfGBWP9jtKI%2FAAAAAAAAAuQ%2FoRcjnKf__fA%2Fs1600%2F1987%252BCityOnFire.jpg&h=7fd0226d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2267578/org/ef56604a8c5c8ed6b22ee9f6556a6845.JPG/hgTdhwhOagLNNHqAhcLjvq6282qsi6FekLeTc5C3k3M?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2267578%2Forg%2Fef56604a8c5c8ed6b22ee9f6556a6845.JPG%2FhgTdhwhOagLNNHqAhcLjvq6282qsi6FekLeTc5C3k3M%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=87d72a07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df8157ae2f2a102b06e492451e12675e26548445","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"係咁多先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff247bab5a8f22b815e8051a231e6b3f37d44d69","tid":2322120,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T18:30:41.000Z","msg":"深夜了"},{"pid":"cc90f5f1cc7629ac67db2d29f29f6d9f51f74371","tid":2322120,"uid":8087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:16:44.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂入面麥嘉做得好好<br />\n睇佢同小鳳姐光頭仔無聊但好好笑<br />\n吉星拱照張艾嘉做嘉劇都好睇<br />\n以前啲電影節奏明快<br />\n但又好有節日氣氛<br />\n隔咗二十年睇都覺得好睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a7417ade503f1a343a188e48adea84d009bf14","tid":2322120,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:40:55.000Z","msg":"秋天的童話當年異類<br />\n文藝片得黎唔悶又貼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c04e94ddc42786078767c77fdaba0591a3fe1e","tid":2322120,"uid":362210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:49:51.000Z","msg":"雙城故事都係聖誕電影，唔講男角，呢套係張曼玉開竅識做戲嘅轉捩點，可以一看<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbeb09171eb8bf1d80fa9458a361a20cf809445","tid":2322120,"uid":20269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T23:46:06.000Z","msg":"秋天的童話暑假上架，吉星拱照就賀歲片黎，龍虎風雲就賀歲第二檔，三部都唔係聖誕片囉"},{"pid":"6b6b537dd56f0c4cc153723330b434c169212c10","tid":2322120,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a7417ade503f1a343a188e48adea84d009bf14","tid":2322120,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:40:55.000Z","msg":"秋天的童話當年異類<br />\n文藝片得黎唔悶又貼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T00:05:43.000Z","msg":"愛情片啫，邊係头藝片"},{"pid":"dfdde4241fc1e7abf7c77d40aa80076b18bce171","tid":2322120,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T00:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1079658/org/f9bc67d4820bc98734cf52ca65230154.jpg/umvb4Aso19_b_KGNUPCxRM2gpnGYWxa7loPMkpaDzJI?v=w1440\" data-th